            "content_html": "<h2>nerfren（2022 CVPR）</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Category：光照反射</li>\n<li>Project: <a href=\"https://bennyguo.github.io/nerfren/\">https://bennyguo.github.io/nerfren/</a></li>\n<li>Code: https</li>\n</ul>\n",
